paragraphs.text:
%pyspark


from pyspark.sql.types import *


input = '/training/flight_pq/*'
kv_output = '/training/flight_kv'

spark = SparkSession \
    .builder \
    .getOrCreate()
    

df = spark.read.format('parquet').option("read.partitions", "4").load(input)  


df.show()

df.write.format('io.iguaz.v3io.spark.sql.kv').option('key', 'id').mode('append').save(kv_output)

%pyspark


from pyspark.sql.types import *


input = '/training/flight_kv'

spark = SparkSession \
    .builder \
    .getOrCreate()
    

schema = StructType([
        StructField('origin_country', StringType(),True),
        StructField('id', StringType(),True),
        StructField('altitude', DoubleType(), True)
       ])

df = spark.read.format('io.iguaz.v3io.spark.sql.kv').schema(schema).option("read.partitions", "4").load(input)  


df.select(df.id,df.origin_country ).filter(df.origin_country=='United States').show()

df.createOrReplaceTempView('flights')
